  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "For achieving a medium effect size (Cohen's f 0.26) on PA and diet based on a previous similar blended study among adults (35), with a statistical power (1-β) of 0.8 and an alpha of 0.05 (38), a total of 91 participants is required for the three groups (IG-1, IG-2, and CG).",
    "Considering the dropout rate of approximately 20% (35), a total of N = 114 participants is required to enable a robust evaluation.",
    "Previous findings indicated that the majority of the face-to-face sessions conducted exercise training and education among older adults without theory backdrop (39).",
    "The participants in the face-toface intervention group will engage in two 60-min sessions per week, including one session for PA at the gym and one for diet at the neighborhood senior center (40) for 10 weeks.",
    "Each PA session will consist of two parts: health education on PA and health (10 minutes) and physical exercise (50 minutes)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
